<item>
            <title>[LU-4960] Investigate support for linux process namespace on server side</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4960</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4476&quot; title=&quot;Add support for linux process namespace&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4476&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4476&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; we need to investigate if there is something that actually needs to be done for linux process namespace on theserver and if so, create a patch for this support.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
